fire_delay.description: How much time before the gun fires, after it is told to do so. (Time is used for aligning the gun's direction)

shell_spawn_count.description: How many shells can we spawn in the stamp we are in?

sync_initial_delay_to_last_minigame.description: [bool]If enabled, when prepping the SEAF Gun for the first time, the stratagem delay will be synced to the delay of the last minigame.
